nvidia-persistenced|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
nvidia-persistenced: nvidia-persistenced (Persistent software state in the NVIDIA driver)
nvidia-persistenced:
nvidia-persistenced: The daemon is used to enable persistent software state in the NVIDIA
nvidia-persistenced: driver. When persistence mode is enabled, the daemon prevents the
nvidia-persistenced: driver from releasing device state when the device is not in use.
nvidia-persistenced: This can improve the startup time of new clients in this scenario.
nvidia-persistenced:
nvidia-persistenced: ftp://download.nvidia.com/XFree86/nvidia-persistenced/
nvidia-persistenced:
nvidia-persistenced:
